OL,3,CCouncillor makes 'remarkable' recovery
OL,4,Cafter life-changing car crash
OL,6,FA Cotswold District Councillor who was
OL,7,Fgiven a 50% chance of survival after a
OL,8,Flife-changing car crash has said he
OL,9,F"can't believe" he's been able to
OL,10,Freturn to work.
OL,12,FTony Dale was on a family holiday in
OL,13,FItaly in July 2024, when the hire car
OL,14,Fhe was travelling in was hit from
OL,15,Fbehind by a lorry near Padua.
OL,17,FHe was crushed in the back seat and
OL,18,Fwas left with a collapsed lung, broken
OL,19,Fribs, a severed carotid artery and
OL,20,Fsevere spinal damage.
