OL,3,CCouncillor makes 'remarkable' recovery
OL,4,Cafter life-changing car crash
OL,6,F"The lorry's bumper smashed my neck,"
OL,7,FCllr Dale said. "I lost three
OL,8,Fvertebrae. It was pretty traumatic."
OL,10,FAfter being airlifted to an Italian
OL,11,Fhospital, Cllr Dale spent three weeks
OL,12,Fin a coma before being transferred to
OL,13,FEngland for treatment at Gloucester
OL,14,FRoyal Hospital.
OL,16,FHe had further treatment at the Spinal
OL,17,FInjuries Unit at Salisbury Hospital,
OL,18,Fand told ITV West Country his recovery
OL,19,Fhas been an emotional rollercoaster.
