OL,3,CCouncillor makes 'remarkable' recovery
OL,4,Cafter life-changing car crash
OL,6,F"I don't think I ever realised just
OL,7,Fhow many tears I had in my body, if
OL,8,FI'm being truthful," he said.
OL,10,F"I've said to so many nurses and
OL,11,Fphysiotherapists, I think I've cried
OL,12,Fmore in the last year than I cried in
OL,13,Fthe entirety of my life."
OL,15,FCllr Dale has now returned to the
OL,16,Fcouncil a year after the crash, and
OL,17,Fsaid "every single person" in his
OL,18,Fcommunity helped in some way.
