OL,3,CCouncillor makes 'remarkable' recovery
OL,4,Cafter life-changing car crash
OL,6,F"My fellow councillors have been
OL,7,Fextraordinary," he said. "But what
OL,8,Fmeant the most is that every single
OL,9,Fcouncillor - across the whole
OL,10,Fpolitical spectrum, green, blue,
OL,11,Fyellow, neutral - sent me messages or
OL,12,Fwell-wishes.
OL,14,F"It made me realise how united we can
OL,15,Fbe."
OL,17,FMr Dale received a standing ovation
OL,18,Ffrom colleagues when he returned to
OL,19,Fwork in the council chamber.
