OL,3,CCouncillor makes 'remarkable' recovery
OL,4,Cafter life-changing car crash
OL,6,FHe said he hopes his recovery will
OL,7,Finspire anyone who suffers similar
OL,8,Finjuries.
OL,10,F"I'm still recovering. I'm 15 kilos
OL,11,Flighter and rebuilding lost muscle
OL,12,Fwith four days a week of neuro-physio.
OL,13,FBut if you believe you can do it, one
OL,14,Fday you will.
OL,16,F"Believe you me. Every day you wake
OL,17,Fup, and you'll smell the fresh air,
OL,18,Fand you just want to do more things.
OL,19,FSo just believe in yourself."
